<emphasis id="79F5EACFFF9ABA69FF3DFF29FE6FEADA" bold="true" box="[151,386,222,248]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Eliomys melanurus</emphasis>
(Wagner, 1839)
</emphasis>
